{"type": "article", "id": 47435, "title": "有144 个抽屉的柜子，据说它就是记忆本身｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-11-20T23:44:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 30138, "name": "抽屉柜"}, {"id": 2284, "name": "桌子"}, {"id": 45663, "name": "笔筒"}, {"id": 776, "name": "锤子"}, {"id": 45664, "name": "螺丝刀"}, {"id": 45665, "name": "Tangent GC"}, {"id": 45666, "name": "Os & Oos"}, {"id": 45667, "name": "Deadgood"}, {"id": 45668, "name": "Abidur Chowdhury"}, {"id": 38401, "name": "Nathan Yong"}, {"id": 45669, "name": "Nika Zupanc"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 110, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171121074407rBnzMNtFiu3aTyxI.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Products with Personality by Deadgood</h3><p>在今年伦敦设计节期间，英国设计品牌 Deadgood 推出了最新系列的家具和灯饰 Products with Personality，其中既有内部团队的设计作品，也有邀请不同设计师的新作。</p><p>Pop 地毯的灵感源自艺术家 Keith Haring 和孟菲斯学派，柔和的色调与大胆的波尔卡圆点或是曲折短线的组合。Spun 吊灯是 2011 款的更新，浑圆的造型添入了新的粉末涂层。Marra 桌子提供三种不同的尺寸，包括咖啡桌、矮桌和高桌。David Irwin 设计的两把椅子配有硬质或软质座椅，希望能够提供舒适的用餐体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120193925R7HfxnPZKFTrh6B1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120193925xle83p9kr2z10AUT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.074219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120193926YbH4DRW7qougnAzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120193927YidRPuSp91Q2ej68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.841406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120193927Pk2cjdrRDIWy0xw4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120193931ZlPWcQn6NoGHjpqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://design-milk.com/deadgood-launches-new-products-with-personality/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Tower Cabinet by Nika Zupanc</h3><p>144 个小型白色抽屉组成的这个圆柱塔，实际上是个创意满满的抽屉柜。它由 CNC 切割胶合板制成，搭配鱼球形黄铜手柄，环绕塔柜的抽屉设计用于存放用户收集的小物件。来自斯洛文尼亚的设计师 <a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/11/20/nika-zupanc-designs-a-tower-of-drawers-for-storing-keepsakes/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nika Zunpanc 说</a>：“这是一个记忆箱，一个迷人的抽屉柜。就像是我们内心世界的精华部分，是我们过去和日常生活记忆的无声见证。”</p><p>在她看来，我们经常会购买、收集很多小物件，其中一些使用，其中一些不用，但想要保留它们，这个柜子便是为收纳这些东西而存在。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194049X2I8uE7kdSgz15el.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194051qWzpIcJHkRoNT7wE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.068105\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194052tMWlVxzqDwgH8h9e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.090948\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201940536qylMNYadO0rhftg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/11/20/nika-zupanc-designs-a-tower-of-drawers-for-storing-keepsakes/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Sputnik by Nathan Yong</h3><p>新加坡工业设计师 Nathan Yong 的新作是笔筒 Sputnik，这是他从自己的童年记忆出发，试图重新诠释的一款老物件，灵感源自旋转陀螺，将有趣和怀旧两种情绪融合在一起，想要重新定义当代的办公用品。</p><p>一个圆柱形的大理石圆锥体总是懒洋洋地倾泻着，上方的四个孔洞用来收纳笔，它造型简单，却能够给书桌添入一点趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194148W0wYEqL9JmbXiODh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017112019414891C5j3dABqZYKDnp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194149WFxJjy2nwImTp0Nq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194149tQqVuCNLFfBcm0WP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nathanyongdesign.com/site/works/sputnik\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nathan Yong Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Instrumentum by Abidur Chowdhury</h3><p>你家的工具箱是不是常常放在橱柜的黑暗角落？很长一段时间这些日常用的工具不会让人与当代设计联系起来，但产品设计师 Abidur Chowdhury 最近在思考的问题是：如何让这些工具变得友好？它提出了一个名为 Instrumentum 的项目，是一把经典造型的锤子和一套螺丝刀，在视觉上给人光滑的感觉，锻钢金属材料的精致质感也透过极简的造型表达出来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194243v4q3xlhUGWBwRbrQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017112019424547VMaWgbJx9stSoP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194246biGkoJyL8e2dmBlI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201942478KJtGr1ZnLRxMqP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194247yztkbuHCR3qa26vp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.abidurchowdhury.com/#/instrumentum/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Abidur Chowdhury</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Concrete Colouring Table by Os &amp; Oos</h3><p>总部设在埃因霍温的设计工作室 Os &amp; Oos，作品一贯都是极简主义风格，擅长尽可能简化各种物品可能的轮廓使之成为几何形态。这款彩色混凝土桌是其最新作品，混凝土制成的底座是整张桌子的稳定器，加上去的弯曲金属轮廓，看似是浮在混凝土底座上，或是黑白色或是金属色的饰面，赋予了桌子不同的性格，也适应于不同场合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194416oYTXtwj2OHS1aCuG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194417jKgEVHsBRQS6NTzw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194418VG3SDu0aONyMxzAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194418uYtc1EIeWKFgPRhd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194418Vcy6hKpGUtzInF8A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666876\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194420zIRakeBCjZH2srM6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.osandoos.com/Colouring-Table-Concrete\" rel=\"nofollow\">Os &amp; Oos</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Tangent GC 100 by Tangent GC</h3><p>TANGENT GC 是瑞典一家服装护理清洁品牌，成立不久便受到众多时尚界明星的青睐，天然有机的衣物护理产品，用温和的方法深层清洁衣物。他们最新推出的 Tangent GC 100 系列，采用纯天然成分制备，他们想到了香水的包装，决定赋予瓶身一个简单的表达方式，白底标签搭配黑体字，只将最必要的信息留在标签上，简明友好。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194503vniyCAXO1U5PqaVr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201945035iFodIyLK3ZJfXwv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194503yd7eYGnm1WvJK5oq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201945039ASXvyEifwRM5nD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120194504SCOont24Le8a1mRQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://minimalissimo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">minimalissimo.com</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}